name: Commander Keen: Aliens Ate My Babysitter!
description:
Only you can rescue Molly from aliens on a far-off planet!!


You are young genius, Billy Blaze. The mean, green Bloogs from Fribbulus Xax have kidnapped your baby sitter and they're going to have her for dinner!

This is a job for your alter-ego - Commander Keen! Armed with your neural stunner and pogo stick, you hop into your homemade rocket and blast off to the rescue!

Travel through beautiful, but dangerous alien territory, exploring factories, guard posts and even an orbiting space station. Weird and wonderful creatures are always present. Some are friendly. Many are not.

On the way, there are puzzles to solve and treasures to discover. but you have to hurry - Molly can't wait much longer!

High quality animation and breathtaking music make a fun and exciting adventure like you've never seen before!
